articles.title: Injured Vinesh Phogat out of Asian Games, Antim to take her place - Hindustan Times
articles.description: The 53kg wrestler, who won gold in the 2018 Asian Games, announced she has suffered a left knee injury and will undergo surgery in Mumbai on Friday.
articles.content: Vinesh Phogat has pulled out of the Asian Games after suffering a knee injury. The defending 53kg champion disclosed her injury on Tuesday and said she will undergo surgery on Friday. A couple of day… [+4140 chars]
